text: WWE Superstars was a professional wrestling television program by WWE. It featured wrestlers from all WWE brands - Raw, SmackDown and, at one time, ECW - competing against each other. The show aired between April 16, 2009 and November 25, 2016 and was replaced on the WWE Network by 205 Live. == References == Category:2009 American television series debuts Category:2010s American television series Superstars Category:2016 American television series endings Category:English-language television programs
